OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774598699
OL,3,CCourt orders campaigner to pay unpaid
OL,4,CSouthern Water wastewater bills
OL,6,FAn environmental campaigner ordered to
OL,7,Fpay unpaid Southern Water wastewater
OL,8,Fbills by a court after a four-year
OL,9,Fboycott, has said the case "will not
OL,10,Fstop us continuing to highlight the
OL,11,Fbasic injustice" for water customers.
OL,13,FJulie Wassmer has withheld paying for
OL,14,Fthe sewage portion of her water bill
OL,15,Fsince 2021, after the company was
OL,16,Fhanded a record #90 million fine for
OL,17,F6,971 unpermitted sewage discharges.
OL,26,@qD@\OUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774598699
OL,3,CCourt orders campaigner to pay unpaid
OL,4,CSouthern Water wastewater bills
OL,6,FSouth East Water, which is the billing
OL,7,Fagent for Southern Water, took the
OL,8,Fcrime writer from Whitstable to court
OL,9,Fover the non-payments.
OL,11,FAt Canterbury County Court on
OL,12,FThursday, District Judge Peter Furness
OL,13,Fruled in favour of claimant South East
OL,14,FWater, saying he simply does not have
OL,15,Fthe power to consider moral or
OL,16,Fenvironmental questions.
OL,18,FHe said: "It is not within my remit
OL,19,Fwithin the context of a small claims
OL,20,Fcourt to decide that point.
OL,26,@zD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774598699
OL,3,CCourt orders campaigner to pay unpaid
OL,4,CSouthern Water wastewater bills
OL,6,F"A bill was produced, it was levied
OL,7,Fand it hasn't been paid.
OL,9,F"Whatever sympathies I may or may not
OL,10,Fhave with your position I am obliged
OL,11,Fto act within the law, it's as simple
OL,12,Fas that."
OL,14,FThe court ordered unpaid bills and
OL,15,Fcosts of #1445.83 to be paid within 56
OL,16,Fdays.
OL,18,FSpeaking outside court, Ms Wassmer
OL,19,Fsaid she was not surprised by the
OL,20,Foutcome but heartened by the judge's
OL,21,Funderstanding of the case.
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774598699
OL,3,CCourt orders campaigner to pay unpaid
OL,4,CSouthern Water wastewater bills
OL,6,F"We have to find another recourse to
OL,7,Fbring justice to water consumers in
OL,8,Fthis country, and my absolute
OL,9,Fdetermination to do that has not been
OL,10,Fdulled by today's experience," she
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"While it was not surprising that the
OL,14,Fjudgment went against us, and for
OL,15,FSouth East Water it will not stop us
OL,16,Fcontinuing to highlight the basic
OL,17,Finjustice that's being suffered by
OL,18,Fwater customers, against water
OL,19,Fcompanies, and to highlight that
OL,20,Fsomething must be done by the
OL,21,FGovernment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@^O]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774598699
OL,3,CCourt orders campaigner to pay unpaid
OL,4,CSouthern Water wastewater bills
OL,6,F"If the law is against the consumers
OL,7,Fin this country regarding water
OL,8,Fcompanies' crimes, then the law has to
OL,9,Fbe changed."
OL,11,FMs Wassmer defended the civil dispute
OL,12,Fagainst herself and her husband
OL,13,FJonathan Kasparian as account holders,
OL,14,Fand said it was "crucial" for water
OL,15,Fcampaigners to highlight Article 6, a
OL,16,Fright to a fair trial, to argue there
OL,17,Fis no real legal recourse to hold
OL,18,Fwater companies to account in the UK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LO]vD@QOUvD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774598699
OL,3,CCourt orders campaigner to pay unpaid
OL,4,CSouthern Water wastewater bills
OL,6,FArguing the case in court, Ms Wassmer,
OL,7,F73, said: "We say it cannot be right
OL,8,Fthat in a modern civic society
OL,9,Fconsumers are forced to pay for
OL,10,Fservices which are not being provided
OL,11,For which seriously pollute our seas
OL,12,Fand waterways and damage our precious
OL,13,Fenvironment, while denying customers a
OL,14,Fmeans of challenging this through the
OL,15,Flegal system.
OL,17,F"As defendants I say we have no court
OL,18,For tribunal in the UK in which we can
OL,19,Ftake this dispute and, we suspect,
OL,20,Fthat may well include this small
OL,21,Fclaims court.
OL,26,@oD@KOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774598699
OL,3,CCourt orders campaigner to pay unpaid
OL,4,CSouthern Water wastewater bills
OL,6,F"To conclude, we do believe a
OL,7,Frejection of the right to have a
OL,8,Fdefence heard contravenes Article 6 of
OL,9,Fthe Human Rights Act (the right to a
OL,10,Ffair trial)."
OL,12,FShe said the couple submitted evidence
OL,13,Fthat existing regulatory bodies are
OL,14,F"not fit for purpose" adding that
OL,15,Fregulator Ofwat "is not a court". She
OL,16,Falso said they hoped the court could
OL,17,Fappreciate that Southern Water's
OL,18,Fabsence from proceedings meant she was
OL,19,F"at a disadvantage" in holding them to
OL,20,Faccount for the non-payment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@MO]vD@AOUvD@UO]wD@QOUwD@`O]{D@
OL,26,AAOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774598699
OL,3,CCourt orders campaigner to pay unpaid
OL,4,CSouthern Water wastewater bills
OL,6,FRepresenting South East Water,
OL,7,Fsolicitor Fergus Poncia said it was
OL,8,F"incorrect" to say they have no other
OL,9,Fplace to go, and they have other
OL,10,Ftribunals and judicial review to raise
OL,11,Fthe points they are making.
OL,13,FJudge Furness also ruled in his
OL,14,Fjudgment there was no question of the
OL,15,Fdefendants being denied a fair trial.
OL,17,F"The defendants can't choose, sadly
OL,18,Ffrom their perspective, what the law
OL,19,Fshould be. I have to work on the basis
OL,20,Fof what the law actually is."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@KO]yD@AOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
