CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774598699
OL,3,CCourt orders campaigner to pay unpaid
OL,4,CSouthern Water wastewater bills
OL,6,FEarlier, on behalf of the claim, Mr
OL,7,FPoncia said in court: "This is about
OL,8,Fan unpaid water services bill.
OL,10,F"We're entitled to collect on behalf
OL,11,Fof Southern Water services."
OL,13,FHe also said Southern Water were fined
OL,14,Ffor illegal spillages 10 years ago and
OL,15,Fthey have since come under new
OL,16,Fownership and are investing #1.6
OL,17,Fbillion in infrastructure.
OL,26,@oD@WOUrD@AOUsD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774598699
OL,3,CCourt orders campaigner to pay unpaid
OL,4,CSouthern Water wastewater bills
OL,6,F"For defendants to say for the
OL,7,Frelevant period of these bills that
OL,8,Fthere has been failure to provide
OL,9,Fadequate wastewater services, all of
OL,10,Ftheir evidence of the period from 10
OL,11,Fyears ago," he said.
OL,13,FA Southern Water spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"We know many households are facing
OL,15,Freal financial pressures, and we never
OL,16,Fwant anyone to worry alone about their
OL,17,Fwater bill. We offer a wide range of
OL,18,Fsupport ` from tailored payment plans
OL,19,Fto significant bill reductions ` and
OL,20,Fwe encourage customers to talk to us
OL,21,Fearly so we can help.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@KO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
