OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774598699
OL,3,CCourt orders campaigner to pay unpaid
OL,4,CSouthern Water wastewater bills
OL,6,F"Customer bills ` along with money
OL,7,Ffrom our shareholders - fund the
OL,8,Fessential improvements our customers
OL,9,Frightly expect. We are delivering our
OL,10,Fbiggest ever investment plan ` around
OL,11,F#8.5 billion ` to improve the
OL,12,Fenvironment, modernise our
OL,13,Finfrastructure and provide a more
OL,14,Freliable service for communities
OL,15,Facross our region.
OL,17,F"These bills also mean we can expand
OL,18,Fsupport for those who need it most,
OL,19,Fwith nearly 200,000 households set to
OL,20,Fbenefit from our social tariff
OL,21,Fschemes."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU}D@IO]
